description: This file is the main entry point for a React frontend application for an online Tic-Tac-Toe platform. It imports React libraries, global styles, the main App component, and core component modules to enable hot reload and build processes. It then initializes and renders the React application into the DOM.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Initializes a React root for rendering the application at the DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React application wrapped in StrictMode into the DOM.
